  ENItemName: Divine Grace
  ENDesc: Duplicates a random unit shard from those you own and summons it to the
    field.
  FRItemName: "Gr\xE2ce divine"
  FRDesc: "Duplique un fragment d'unit\xE9 al\xE9atoire parmi ceux que vous poss\xE9dez
    et l'invoque sur le terrain."
  ITItemName: Grazia divina
  ITDesc: "Duplica un frammento di unit\xE0 casuale tra quelli in tuo possesso e
    lo evoca sul campo."
  DEItemName: "G\xF6ttliche Gnade"
  DEDesc: "Dupliziert ein zuf\xE4lliges Einheitenfragment aus Ihrem Bestand und beschw\xF6rt
    es aufs Feld."
  ESItemName: Gracia divina
  ESDesc: Duplica un fragmento de unidad aleatorio entre los que posees y lo invoca
    en el campo.
  JAItemName: "\u795E\u306E\u6069\u5BF5"
  JADesc: "\u6240\u6301\u3057\u3066\u3044\u308B\u30E6\u30CB\u30C3\u30C8\u306E\u7834\u7247\u306E\u4E2D\u304B\u3089\u30E9\u30F3\u30C0\u30E0\u30671\u3064\u3092\u8907\u88FD\u3057\u3066\u30D5\u30A3\u30FC\u30EB\u30C9\u306B\u53EC\u559A\u3057\u307E\u3059\u3002"
  PT_BRItemName: "Gra\xE7a Divina"
  PT_BRDesc: "Duplica um fragmento de unidade aleat\xF3rio dentre os que voc\xEA
    possui e o invoca no campo."
  RUItemName: "\u0411\u043E\u0436\u044C\u044F \u043C\u0438\u043B\u043E\u0441\u0442\u044C"
  RUDesc: "\u0414\u0443\u0431\u043B\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0435\u0442 \u0441\u043B\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0439\u043D\u044B\u0439
